        <span id="BookReviewTitle" class="BookReviewTitle">Flying High: How JetBlue Founder and CEO David Neeleman Beats the Competition... Even in the World's Most Turbulent Industry</span>
        <div class="ItemDetail">By
          <span id="Authors">James  Wynbrandt</span></div>
